trans-unit.resname: On a crisp autumn morning, the leaves rustled softly as a gentle breeze swept through the trees. The sun peeked through the branches, casting dappled shadows on the forest floor. Birds chirped merrily, their songs echoing in the tranquil air. A small stream gurgled nearby, its waters crystal clear and inviting. It was a perfect day for a leisurely stroll in the woods, soaking in the sights and sounds of nature.
trans-unit.source: On a crisp autumn morning, the leaves rustled softly as a gentle breeze swept through the trees. The sun peeked through the branches, casting dappled shadows on the forest floor. Birds chirped merrily, their songs echoing in the tranquil air. A small stream gurgled nearby, its waters crystal clear and inviting. It was a perfect day for a leisurely stroll in the woods, soaking in the sights and sounds of nature.
trans-unit.target: Par une journée d'été brûlante, alors que le soleil brillait intensément dans un ciel sans nuages, une petite brise caressait doucement les feuilles des arbres. Les enfants riaient et jouaient dans le parc, tandis que les oiseaux chantaient gaiement. Au loin, on entendait le doux murmure d'une rivière qui coulait paisiblement. C'était une journée parfaite pour se détendre et profiter de la beauté de la nature.

trans-unit.resname: This service includes basic cleaning of residential or commercial spaces. It includes sweeping, mopping floors, dusting surfaces, cleaning bathrooms and kitchens, and emptying garbage cans. It's ideal for small houses, apartments or offices.

trans-unit.target: Ce service comprend le nettoyage de base des espaces résidentiels ou commerciaux. Il inclut le balayage, le lavage des sols, le dépoussiérage des surfaces, le nettoyage des salles de bains et des cuisines, ainsi que la vidange des poubelles. Il est idéal pour les petites maisons, les appartements ou les bureaux de petite taille.

trans-unit.resname: This service offers a wider range of cleaning services, tailored to customers' more specific needs. In addition to basic cleaning tasks, it includes window cleaning, carpet and rug cleaning, deep dusting of furniture, as well as appliance cleaning. It is suitable for larger residences, medium-sized offices and high-end commercial spaces.
